mindmap
  root((diagramkit<br/>Principles))
    One Chromium
      Shared BrowserPool
      Graphviz is WASM only
    Engine Registry
      Extension mapping
      Engine profiles
      Renderer dispatch
    SVG-First
      Vector is canonical
      Raster via sharp
    Light + Dark
      Both themes default
      Theme suffix naming
    Incremental Builds
      SHA-256 manifest
      Skip unchanged
    Layered Config
      Defaults → Global → Env → Local → CLI
    Atomic Writes
      .tmp + rename
    Extension Detection
      Longest match first
